---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import RelatedArticles from '../../components/RelatedArticles.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="敏肌护理指南 — 海得宝 MarTempo" description="敏感肌的日常护理方法：饮食生活习惯调整、常见误区纠正，科学护理敏感肌改善肌肤状态。">
  <Nav />
  <main>
    <!-- ── Hero ── -->
    <section class="guide-hero">
      <div class="guide-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="section-inner">
        <nav class="guide-breadcrumb" aria-label="面包屑导航">
          <a href="/">首页</a>
          <span class="sep">›</span>
          <a href="/skincare/knowledge/">敏感性肌肤知识</a>
          <span class="sep">›</span>
          <span class="current">敏肌护理指南</span>
        </nav>
        <div class="guide-hero-content">
          <div class="guide-hero-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <h1 class="guide-hero-title">敏肌护理指南</h1>
          <p class="guide-hero-subtitle">科学护理敏感肌，改善肌肤状态</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── 5. 饮食及生活习惯 ── -->
    <section class="guide-section reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="guide-block">
          <div class="guide-block-text">
            <h2 class="guide-section-title">敏感肌饮食及生活习惯</h2>
            <div class="guide-tips">
              <div class="guide-tip">
                <div class="guide-tip-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="guide-tip-title">做好防晒</h3>
                  <p class="guide-tip-body">敏感肌本身肌肤屏障处于破损阶段，对于外界刺激抵御能力薄弱。若因肌肤状态不稳定无法使用防晒产品，也要做好物理防晒（遮阳伞、防晒帽、防晒衣等）。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="guide-tip">
                <div class="guide-tip-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="guide-tip-title">清淡饮食</h3>
                  <p class="guide-tip-body">敏感肌人群更易过敏，过敏期间需要注意减少海鲜、花生等高蛋白饮食，注意补充维生素含量较多的饮食，提升免疫力。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="guide-tip">
                <div class="guide-tip-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="guide-tip-title">减少摩擦</h3>
                  <p class="guide-tip-body">敏感肌不宜频繁去角质，应增厚角质、提升肌肤抵抗力。护理手法上需要减少不必要的摩擦及按摩动作。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="guide-tip">
                <div class="guide-tip-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="guide-tip-title">精简护肤</h3>
                  <p class="guide-tip-body">使用温和安全的护肤品，精简护肤步骤，尽量不用酒精、香精等刺激成分。选择配方精简、无刺激添加的专业修护产品。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-block-image">
            <img src="/assets/skincare/1551184451.jpg" alt="健康生活方式示意" class="guide-img guide-img--landscape" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── 6. 敏感肌误区 ── -->
    <section class="guide-section guide-section--alt reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="guide-block-center">
          <h2 class="guide-section-title">敏感肌误区</h2>
          <p class="guide-section-body lead">错误的护理方式可能让敏感问题雪上加霜，听听海得宝怎么说。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="guide-myths">
          <div class="guide-myth">
            <div class="guide-myth-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="guide-myth-header">
              <span class="guide-myth-label">误区一</span>
              <h3 class="guide-myth-title">敏感期停用护肤品，让肌肤自愈</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="guide-myth-body">很多人认为敏感发作时应停用所有护肤品，靠皮肤自身修护就能好转。但敏感肌的核心问题并非单一屏障受损，底层炎症才是反复敏感的根源。若完全放弃护理，炎症无法得到干预，敏感状态会持续甚至加重。</p>
            <div class="guide-myth-correct">
              <span class="guide-myth-correct-label">正确做法</span>
              <p class="guide-myth-correct-body">选用配方精简、无刺激添加的专业修护护肤品，在舒缓表层不适的同时，帮助抑制底层炎症，逐步修护皮肤屏障。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-myth">
            <div class="guide-myth-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="guide-myth-header">
              <span class="guide-myth-label">误区二</span>
              <h3 class="guide-myth-title">敏感期频繁敷补水，用面膜缓解干燥</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="guide-myth-body">干燥脱皮时，多数人会用密集敷面膜来急救，但这种做法反而会加重皮肤负担。过度敷面膜会导致皮肤过度水合，使肌肤细胞间连接松弛，破坏屏障完整性，进而诱发或加重炎症反应。</p>
            <div class="guide-myth-correct">
              <span class="guide-myth-correct-label">正确做法</span>
              <p class="guide-myth-correct-body">以温和的保湿乳霜替代面膜，通过持续锁水维持皮肤水润状态，同时配合具有抗炎功效的成分（例贻贝钙肽CAPCS），从根源改善敏感。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-myth">
            <div class="guide-myth-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="guide-myth-header">
              <span class="guide-myth-label">误区三</span>
              <h3 class="guide-myth-title">用磨砂洗面奶 / 频繁去角质"焕肤"</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="guide-myth-body">部分敏感肌人群会误以为皮肤粗糙、泛红是清洁不足导致，进而使用磨砂类洁面产品或频繁去角质。敏感肌本身屏障脆弱，物理摩擦会直接损伤本就薄弱的皮脂膜，让皮肤失去天然防护。</p>
            <div class="guide-myth-correct">
              <span class="guide-myth-correct-label">正确做法</span>
              <p class="guide-myth-correct-body">选用温和的慕斯洁面产品，每日清洁1-2次即可。日常无需刻意去角质，让皮肤屏障自然修护。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <RelatedArticles currentSlug="guide" />
  <Footer />

  <script>
    import '../../scripts/reveal.js';
  </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Hero ── */
  .guide-hero {
    padding: 120px var(--content-padding) var(--space-4xl);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .guide-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, oklch(96% 0.015 185) 0%, oklch(98% 0.008 185) 50%, #ffffff 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .guide-hero > .section-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .guide-breadcrumb {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .guide-breadcrumb a {
    color: oklch(50% 0.01 260 / 0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .guide-breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: var(--color-brand);
  }

  .guide-breadcrumb .sep {
    margin: 0 6px;
    color: oklch(50% 0.01 260 / 0.5);
  }

  .guide-breadcrumb .current {
    color: oklch(35% 0.015 260 / 0.7);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .guide-hero-accent {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-brand);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .guide-hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .guide-hero-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--guide-text, var(--color-text-soft));
    max-width: 40ch;
  }

  /* ── Shared section ── */
  .guide-section {
    --guide-text: oklch(28% 0.025 260);
    padding: var(--space-6xl) var(--content-padding);
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .guide-section--alt {
    background: var(--color-bg-light);
  }

  .guide-block-center {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .guide-section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .guide-section-body.lead {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--guide-text, var(--color-text-soft));
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* ── Image + text block ── */
  .guide-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .guide-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .guide-img--landscape { aspect-ratio: 4/3; }

  /* ── Tips ── */
  .guide-tips {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .guide-tip {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .guide-tip-dot {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-brand);
  }

  .guide-tip-title {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .guide-tip-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--guide-text, var(--color-text-soft));
  }

  /* ── Myths ── */
  .guide-myths {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .guide-myth {
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .guide-myth-accent {
    width: 28px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-brand);
    border-radius: 1px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .guide-myth-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: oklch(60% 0.12 30);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .guide-myth-title {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
  }

  .guide-myth-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--guide-text, var(--color-text-soft));
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .guide-myth-correct {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }

  .guide-myth-correct-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-brand);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .guide-myth-correct-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--guide-text, var(--color-text-soft));
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .guide-block {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .guide-block-image {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .guide-myths {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .guide-section {
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--content-padding);
    }

    .guide-hero {
      padding: 100px var(--content-padding) var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .guide-myths {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
